name: Natasha
story: A doctor from the Underworld and a caregiver of children.Alongside her kindness and caring, she also has a hidden dangerous side.

skills.name: Behind the Kindness
skills.description: Deals minor Physical DMG to a single enemy.

skills.name: Love, Heal, and Choose
skills.description: Restores HP for a single ally and provides Healing Over Time to them.

skills.name: Innervation
skills.description: When healing allies with low HP, increases Outgoing Healing. This effect also works on continuous healing.

skills.name: Hypnosis Research
skills.description: Attacks the enemy. After entering battle, deals minor Physical DMG to a random single enemy, with a high chance to inflict Weaken to all enemy targets.

eidolons.name: Pharmacology Expertise
eidolons.description: After being attacked, if the current HP percentage is 30% or lower, heals self for 1 time to restore HP by an amount equal to 15% of Max HP plus 400. This effect can only be triggered 1 time per battle.

eidolons.name: Clinical Research
eidolons.description: When Natasha uses her Ultimate, grant continuous healing for 1 turn(s) to allies whose HP is at 30% or lower. And at the beginning of their turn, their HP is restored by an amount equal to 6% of Natasha's Max HP plus 160.

eidolons.name: The Right Cure
eidolons.description: Skill Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. 15.Basic ATK Lv. +1, up to a maximum of Lv. 10.

eidolons.name: Miracle Cure
eidolons.description: After being attacked, regenerates 5 extra Energy.

eidolons.name: Preventive Treatment
eidolons.description: Ultimate Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. 15.Talent Lv. +2, up to a maximum of Lv. 15.

eidolons.name: Doctor's Grace
eidolons.description: Natasha's Basic ATK additionally deals Physical DMG equal to 40% of her Max HP.
